Sync & corrections by honeybunny
& chamallow www.addic7ed.com

00:05.525 --> 00:08.528
(Motor whirring)

00:11.998 --> 00:14.100
Hospitality, this is Tango Five.

00:14.167 --> 00:16.035
We're four mikes out,
requesting hot extract.

00:16.102 --> 00:18.104
Hopper, stay with me.

00:21.541 --> 00:23.042
Hospitality, this is Tango Five.

00:23.109 --> 00:26.045
We're at the rendezvous. Over.

00:26.112 --> 00:28.281
Hospitality, this is Tango Five.

00:28.347 --> 00:29.982
Do you read?

00:31.217 --> 00:33.986
Hospitality, do you read?

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:47.533 --> 00:48.668
(Radio beeps)

00:48.734 --> 00:49.880
(Beeping stops)

00:50.000 --> 00:52.305
Helm, ready for dive. We're
not gonna be here long.

00:52.371 --> 00:53.706
Chief of the boat,

00:53.773 --> 00:55.521
you get those SEALs on
board as fast as you can.

00:55.641 --> 00:57.009
I have multiple contacts.

00:57.450 --> 00:59.219
Something big outside the lane.
Classifying now.

00:59.644 --> 01:02.247
Gentlemen, we have just surfaced
in the middle of a highway.

01:02.314 --> 01:03.882
Let me know if anything acts pissy.

01:03.949 --> 01:05.750
Lieutenant Shepard,

01:05.817 --> 01:07.452
I need three good ways out of here.

01:07.519 --> 01:08.687
Aye-aye, sir.

01:08.753 --> 01:09.654
Sir, big boy at sea

01:09.721 --> 01:11.056
is a Pakistani Zulfiquar class frigate

01:11.122 --> 01:13.158
turning on our position.

01:13.225 --> 01:15.193
Captain, the hatch is shut.
Straight board.

01:15.313 --> 01:16.995
Submerge the boat, lieutenant.

01:17.062 --> 01:18.663
Dive! Dive!

01:18.730 --> 01:20.699
Venting forward. Venting aft.

01:20.765 --> 01:24.436
Ahead two-thirds. Come to 2-7-5.

01:24.502 --> 01:26.438
Lieutenant Shepard, you have the conn.

01:26.504 --> 01:28.240
X.O., you're with me.

01:28.306 --> 01:29.708
Sir.

01:29.774 --> 01:30.642
Relax, lieutenant.

01:30.709 --> 01:32.277
We aren't actually at war.

01:32.344 --> 01:33.612
Just make him realize

01:33.678 --> 01:36.348
how incredibly dead he'd be if we were.

01:37.882 --> 01:40.018
(Man) Captain.

01:40.085 --> 01:42.220
X.O.

01:42.735 --> 01:43.954
(Monitor beeping rhythmically)

01:44.074 --> 01:44.767
Thanks, chief.

01:44.887 --> 01:47.058
You bet, son.

01:48.660 --> 01:50.729
Careful with these boys.

01:50.795 --> 01:53.164
They're wound tight.

01:55.075 --> 01:57.389
Gil Langston, captain.
Thank you for the pickup.

01:57.509 --> 01:59.304
Anytime. How's your man?

01:59.371 --> 02:00.639
Needs a hospital.

02:00.705 --> 02:01.973
We're headed towards
the Eisenhower group

02:02.040 --> 02:03.275
to test a new piece of equipment.

02:03.341 --> 02:05.076
Five hours, we'll be in
range of the choppers.

02:05.143 --> 02:07.245
That's some serious heat
that came after you guys.

02:07.312 --> 02:10.482
Anything we should know?

02:10.548 --> 02:12.851
Once again, captain, thank
you for the pickup.

02:12.918 --> 02:15.887
(People speaking indistinctly)

02:15.954 --> 02:18.890
You had to ask, didn't you?

02:18.957 --> 02:20.725
(Monitor beeping rhythmically)

02:20.792 --> 02:23.828
What the hell happened back there?

02:25.964 --> 02:27.332
Cortez, Reynolds,

02:27.399 --> 02:29.067
don't make me chase you down.

02:29.134 --> 02:31.703
(Man speaking indistinctly over P.A.)

02:31.770 --> 02:33.939
1400 hours, day 56 of the tour,

02:34.005 --> 02:36.541
this is a meeting to
allow you to inform me

02:36.608 --> 02:38.410
if any member of the crew
has acted towards you

02:38.476 --> 02:39.978
in a manner offensive to yourself

02:40.045 --> 02:41.646
or to the other female
members of your rack,

02:41.713 --> 02:43.648
or in a manner contrary... (Laughs)

02:43.715 --> 02:45.450
To the rules and regulations
of Navy policy.

02:45.517 --> 02:46.651
But how are you...

02:46.718 --> 02:48.119
how are you supposed
to do sensitivity duty

02:48.186 --> 02:49.654
and you all talking about "racks"?

02:49.721 --> 02:50.989
(Chuckles)

02:51.056 --> 02:53.291
Just answer the question, Cortez.

02:53.358 --> 02:56.328
No one has offended,
bothered, copped a feel,

02:56.448 --> 02:59.062
or otherwise molested
any member of my rack.

02:59.182 --> 03:00.722
Love these weekly chats, though.

03:00.842 --> 03:02.404
Welcome to the Navy, sailor.

03:03.777 --> 03:05.245
(Man) No, no, no, no, man, look.

03:05.312 --> 03:06.880
He's like, he's like...

03:06.947 --> 03:10.217
(Beatboxing)

03:10.283 --> 03:11.585
(Chuckles) Stupid.

03:11.652 --> 03:12.994
It's a feeling, V.
It's not intellectual.

03:12.995 --> 03:14.035
Stupid.

03:14.155 --> 03:15.990
No, I mean, look, you're...
you're from Arizona, right?

03:16.110 --> 03:17.567
- Yeah.
- Okay, I'm not even being offensive,

03:17.698 --> 03:19.200
'cause I got a cousin from Tucson...
(Laughs)

03:19.267 --> 03:21.035
But it just means that you
have no idea what he's doing.

03:21.101 --> 03:21.791
I have no idea?

03:21.911 --> 03:23.521
No. You think he's all "ho
this" and "bitch that"...

03:23.541 --> 03:24.352
that's not what I said.

03:24.372 --> 03:25.906
And it's just not the case.
It's just not the...

03:25.973 --> 03:27.712
Really? Are you guys still at this?

03:27.832 --> 03:29.492
X.O., permission to shoot

03:29.612 --> 03:31.579
petty Officer Brannan in the head.

03:32.262 --> 03:33.815
Permission granted.

03:36.064 --> 03:37.499
Closest thing to an actual engagement

03:37.565 --> 03:39.401
we'll probably ever see,
and he gives her the conn?

03:39.467 --> 03:40.902
Just hands it over,

03:40.969 --> 03:42.837
like "Here you go, sweetheart.
You have fun with that."

03:42.904 --> 03:44.539
Yeah, nice being an admiral's kid.

03:44.606 --> 03:45.707
(Chuckles) Yeah.

03:45.774 --> 03:47.108
(Imitates female voice) "Oh, captain,

03:47.175 --> 03:48.977
are you really gonna let
me drive the boat?"

03:51.046 --> 03:52.414
Ma'am.

03:52.480 --> 03:54.149
(Man speaks indistinctly over P.A.)

03:54.215 --> 03:56.151
X.O., captain wants to see you

03:56.217 --> 03:57.752
in his quarters when you're done.

03:57.819 --> 04:00.522
Mm-hmm.

04:00.588 --> 04:02.624
(Equipment beeping, people
speaking indistinctly)

04:02.691 --> 04:04.761
X.O. on the conn.

04:04.881 --> 04:07.629
(Man) X.O. on the conn.

04:07.696 --> 04:09.864
(Lowered voice) Your
guys Lawrence and Stern,

04:09.931 --> 04:11.866
they're busting Grace's balls.

04:11.933 --> 04:13.501
(Chuckles)

04:13.568 --> 04:17.839
I wasn't aware of the
presence of those, sir.

04:17.906 --> 04:20.208
Consider it taken care of.

04:20.274 --> 04:22.577
Thank you.

04:22.644 --> 04:24.512
(Knock on door)

04:24.579 --> 04:26.581
Come in. (Door opens)

04:26.648 --> 04:27.749
(Man speaks indistinctly over P.A.)

04:27.816 --> 04:29.384
(Door closes)

04:29.451 --> 04:30.552
How's Jeffrey doing?

04:30.618 --> 04:32.654
You must be proud.

04:32.721 --> 04:34.489
Yeah, he says he's jealous of me,

04:34.556 --> 04:36.324
being surrounded by water.

04:36.391 --> 04:37.525
(Chuckles)

04:37.592 --> 04:39.478
Guess it's pretty dry where they are.

04:39.598 --> 04:41.396
Listen, Cameron's been
tracking the fleet.

04:41.463 --> 04:42.564
He's doing that thing that he does.

04:42.630 --> 04:43.647
What do you know about

04:43.767 --> 04:45.408
the Eisenhower group changing course?

04:48.069 --> 04:50.004
Here's the latest surface grab.

04:50.071 --> 04:52.440
D.C. is falling apart.

04:52.507 --> 04:54.209
(Woman) Four generals
resigned in protest,

04:54.275 --> 04:56.182
calling the president's
policies reckless

04:56.302 --> 04:57.479
and irresponsible.

04:57.545 --> 04:58.747
As the impeachment vote approaches,

04:58.813 --> 05:00.382
the embattled president...

05:00.448 --> 05:02.017
(TV beeps)

05:02.083 --> 05:05.954
Ronald Reagan fires all the
air traffic controllers.

05:06.021 --> 05:07.822
And his guys come to him, and they say,

05:07.889 --> 05:10.065
"Mr. President, why did you
go and do such a thing?

05:10.185 --> 05:12.861
Everyone's gonna think you're crazy."

05:12.927 --> 05:14.729
And Reagan...

05:14.796 --> 05:16.564
He points out the window
of the Oval Office

05:16.631 --> 05:17.499
toward Russia,

05:17.565 --> 05:19.768
and he says, "That's right.

05:19.834 --> 05:23.405
That's exactly what I need
that bastard to think."

05:23.471 --> 05:25.040
Uh, what are we celebrating?

05:25.106 --> 05:26.775
You see, everyone knew
Brezhnev was crazy.

05:26.841 --> 05:28.576
Hell, he invaded Afghanistan.

05:28.643 --> 05:31.813
The problem was, nobody
knew if Reagan was.

05:31.880 --> 05:34.249
And if there's one absolute truth

05:34.315 --> 05:36.584
to being the man with your
finger on the button,

05:36.651 --> 05:37.819
that's it.

05:37.886 --> 05:39.988
They have to think you're crazy.

05:40.055 --> 05:42.490
(Chuckles)
Here's to being 500 feet under

05:42.557 --> 05:44.492
and half a world away from it all.

05:44.559 --> 05:45.827
(Clinks)

05:45.894 --> 05:47.929
(Chuckles)

05:51.433 --> 05:54.069
Ahh.

06:00.608 --> 06:02.711
Will Frears is looking for a second

06:02.777 --> 06:05.714
at Naval Command, Virginia.

06:05.780 --> 06:07.382
I recommended you.

06:08.621 --> 06:10.618
You can take a week with
Christine once we get back

06:10.685 --> 06:12.053
and make the move.

06:12.120 --> 06:13.488
Marcus... (Chuckles)

06:13.555 --> 06:15.490
Whatever you think you owe me, Sam,

06:15.557 --> 06:18.026
you've paid a hundred times over.

06:18.093 --> 06:19.527
You have a wife.

06:19.594 --> 06:22.397
Go home. Take a desk.

06:22.464 --> 06:24.799
Start a family.

06:28.303 --> 06:30.304
(Door closes)

06:39.747 --> 06:41.148
Chief of the boat.

06:41.215 --> 06:42.983
Listen, Grace, um...

06:43.050 --> 06:45.185
Lawrence and Stern,

06:45.252 --> 06:48.188
they'll be pulling
latrine duty for a week.

06:48.255 --> 06:49.556
I just hope you understand,

06:49.623 --> 06:52.459
it's not about you being a woman.

06:52.526 --> 06:55.262
I just haven't earned their respect.

06:55.329 --> 06:56.931
Well...

06:56.997 --> 06:58.465
Two weeks latrine duty for both of them,

06:58.532 --> 07:01.402
and, C.O.B., you address
me by my rank or ma'am,

07:01.468 --> 07:03.203
not my first name.

07:13.466 --> 07:15.024
Lieutenant Shepard, position report.

07:15.144 --> 07:17.351
1,012 clicks south west
of Sri Lanka, sir.

07:17.418 --> 07:19.358
Crossing the equator in... (Beeping)

07:19.478 --> 07:20.882
